Class AlertEngine:
  check(self, scores, state) -> list of alert dicts:
    Returns list of active alerts. Each alert:
    {"level": "warn"|"critical", "code": "SHORT_CODE", "message": "human readable"}
    
    Check these conditions:
    - pwr < 30: critical, "LOW_BATTERY", "Battery critically low"
    - pwr < 50: warn, "BATTERY_WARN", "Battery below 50%"
    - gps < 40: critical, "GPS_POOR", "Poor GPS signal"
    - ekf < 40: critical, "EKF_UNHEALTHY", "EKF health degraded"
    - imu < 40: critical, "IMU_FAULT", "IMU readings abnormal"
    - com < 40: critical, "COMMS_LOST", "Communication link degraded"
    - composite < 50: warn, "HEALTH_WARN", "Overall drone health low"
    - composite < 30: critical, "HEALTH_CRITICAL", "Drone health critical"

